00:00:17.400 --> 00:00:24.360
cool Opera, heavy-metal t-shirt, very nice.
So everyone knows what Opera is. So I wanted

00:00:24.360 --> 00:00:30.600
to jump in, what kind of things are you involved
in right now. What are some new interesting

00:00:30.600 --> 00:00:32.870
things that Opera is working in its desk?
