Dragonfly which is a Web developer tool. So

00:00:37.440 --> 00:00:41.219
it's similar [INDISTINCT] like Firebird, except
this is architected that it can work on any

00:00:41.219 --> 00:00:46.319
device so you can use it on your mobile phone
and you connect through a proxy to the desktop

00:00:46.319 --> 00:00:50.620
computer instead of having to use emulators
and things like that. You can debug directly

00:00:50.620 --> 00:00:55.519
from the phone. So it's something very interesting.
We're doing also Opera widgets is something

00:00:55.519 --> 00:00:59.940
which is getting big take off in the mobile
space with things like phone to phone and

00:00:59.940 --> 00:01:02.499
T-mobile, just...
&gt;&gt; MCCATHIENEVILE: So they're no longer Opera

00:01:02.499 --> 00:01:07.900
widgets, like W3C widgets, 'cause two or three
ECO, when every man and their dog was building

00:01:07.900 --> 00:01:11.909
a widget or a gadget or whatever you want
to call them, Opera went to W3C and said,

00:01:11.909 --> 00:01:16.869
"Everyone is doing this. Let's make one version
that everybody can use, so developers don't

00:01:16.869 --> 00:01:23.700
have to code eight times." And that's something
we're doing. We're doing some other stuff.

00:01:23.700 --> 00:01:29.149
We're doing--we put out a geo-location builds,
like, the Google contributed an editor and

00:01:29.149 --> 00:01:34.049
the spec, Opera has done implementation of
geo-location [INDISTINCT] so we made a build

00:01:34.049 --> 00:01:40.829
that you can do that. We're working on 3D
Canvas being Chronos which is, you know, with

00:01:40.829 --> 00:01:44.939
Mozilla and looking at the O3D and different
ways of doing that. There's a whole heap of

00:01:44.939 --> 00:01:47.840
stuff about access to your platforms.
&gt;&gt; NEUBERG: Right.

00:01:47.840 --> 00:01:51.240
&gt;&gt; MCCATHIENEVILE: So being able to use the
camera or being able to send an SMS if you've

00:01:51.240 --> 00:01:58.850
got a phone connection or a network like a
phone card, like, any of that, your laptop,

00:01:58.850 --> 00:02:05.549
being able to, you access information like
the address book or your calendar stuff. So

00:02:05.549 --> 00:02:13.530
you can do things like have your Web information
and your local information connect to each

00:02:13.530 --> 00:02:17.530
other and synchronize better, just making
it more flexible.

00:02:17.530 --> 00:02:21.820
